  "synopsis": "The story tells of an unscrupulous merchant, Boss Wan, who plots to seize a prosperous fishing village and places a treacherous net in the sea. A young fisherman named Manjiang thwarts his scheme… \"A small story, a profound lesson,\" the entire tale interprets the unique customs and emotional expressions of people living along the river and sea, as well as their frugal, diligent, peaceful, and dedicated lifestyle.\n\n(Source: Tencent, translated)",
